*[[Vernon Lewis]], [[Jermaine Holt]] and [[Nathaniel Perry (stuntman)|Nathaniel Perry]] were stunt doubles for [[Idris Elba]] in the role of Heimdall.
*[[Ade Akisanya]] was a stand-in for [[Idris Elba]] in the role of Heimdall.
*[[Roberto Harrison]] was a picture double for [[Idris Elba]] in the role of Heimdall.
